 Episode 5 of Ndani TV’s web series “Ratings” is here and this one is tagged ‘Getaway Car’. In this hilarious episode of “Ratings​”, FJ finds himself in a precarious situation when he unwittingly picks up a trio who seem to be up to no good. The web series which follows the hilarious adventures of a taxi driver, FJ and features Michael Sani Amanesi, Jide Kosoko, Adekunle Bryan, is written by Bode Asiyanbi. Enjoy! 